Genetic evidence supports a range extension for the Brazilian cownose ray 
Rhinoptera brasiliensis in the western North Atlantic.

Weber HK(1), Jones CM(2), Ajemian MJ(3), McCallister MP(3), Winner BL(4), 
Poulakis GR(5), Bethea DM(6), Hollensead LD(7), Zapf D(8), Swenson JD(9), Hendon 
JM(10), Daly-Engel TS(11), Phillips NM(1).

Author information:
(1)School of Biological, Environmental and Earth Sciences, The University of 
